videoDetails.Title: MASTER Desmos Calculator in 2024 and Change Your Math Game!
videoDetails.Description:
Learn how to use the free Desmos graphing calculator.  Learn how to graph equations, do math calculations, and access features of Desmos.  Type equations of lines, math expressions including fractions, exponents and square roots, and change the graph settings are all easy in Desmos.

Desmos is free at:  https://www.desmos.com/ 

▶ *Watch* 
Desmos Playlist:  https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLJEsnGh2PECimzd8TN5nxED2Q_XclUDjJ 

*Chapters*
0:00 Desmos Graph Settings
1:45 Table in Desmos
2:34 Intersection Points
3:35 Computing in Desmos
